Package application.model

Class DatabaseInterface

java.lang.Object
application.model.DatabaseInterface
public class DatabaseInterface extends Object
A class that allows JDBC connection to the SQL databases. Will be called by object and controller functions.
Author:
Justin Van Nimwegen - 930005547, Aaron Su - 930006201 315 - Project 2
